Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:03.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:11.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:13.78,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,祝您武運昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:16.04,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,櫻庭學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:19.14,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,看起來應該沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:30.64,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真讓我吃驚 這就是你的真正力量麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:32.30,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:35.62,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,簡直就像是怪物 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.01,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,只是比力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.40,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Double Cast•Force Field•Thunder Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.21,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:58.30,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼力量 這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:06.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Quick Cast・Fog cloud・Modifier・Effective Area・Colossal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:13.86,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 里見孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:24.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,想要戰勝他必須要得到那間106室的力量才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:12.48,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,咦 我這是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.28,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,孝太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.24,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:24.15,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,對了 由莉佳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.43,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧 櫻庭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,她只是暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.17,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,她沒事的 你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:39.10,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好的 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.69,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 在那之後發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.39,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳倒下之後我就什麼都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.37,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你沒印象了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.70,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是的 什麼都沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:56.21,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣麼 既然這樣就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.16,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:04.23,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見 櫻庭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,結果還是沒回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:16.40,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,幸好第五節課是自習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.56,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 還是聯繫一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我打過電話了 不過沒有信號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,要是擔心的話 我可以去找他們呵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.72,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,哼 我才沒有擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:34.30,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那我得去考慮舞臺的構成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.61,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,別來打擾我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.13,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,問題是結尾部分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.84,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,白銀公主確實是愛著青騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.11,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但青騎士又究竟是怎樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:48.79,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,{＠\an7}※於是接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:53.73,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,如果愛著她的話應該會接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.14,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,接吻的青騎士和白銀公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:05.43,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我要和那種粗鄙的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:09.58,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是我要給他做演技指導
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:16.73,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我要和他做戀人之間做的那種令人窒息的深吻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:21.60,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,殿下 您怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.10,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.42,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不好 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:27.54,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:33.94,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎 真希她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:35.88,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 她逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.42,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我讓早苗去叫大夥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:40.40,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,等她們來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.11,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,沒這時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.83,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳同學 別勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:49.10,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 我可是愛與勇氣的魔法少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.31,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:54.09,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真希一定在106室那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:55.84,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,得馬上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.95,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你這副樣子是沒法戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:03.04,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,至少再在這恢復一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:04.16,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我也會陪你一起戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.75,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不過最關鍵的你是這副樣子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,可沒有勝算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.51,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,而且我有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.31,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,關於你的… 魔法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.70,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:30.48,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:36.66,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那把劍是通過控制了積存在這裡的一部分魔力創造出來的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,只是一部分就有那樣的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:44.90,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,只要解析出里見孝太郎所使用的術式再搶過控制權
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:47.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥力的差距就能逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:52.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我好像是有使用魔法的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:56.45,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,有一天突然就被察覺到的魔物所襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:08:02.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那時救下我的就是身為魔法少女的娜娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:06.23,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是你的救命恩人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:06.97,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:12.62,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我想要向娜娜小姐報恩所以就開始給她做幫手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.28,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,雖然她不讓我參加戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.14,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不過我一直幫她做飯查資料之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:23.09,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜小姐是弗沙裡亞人沒有戶籍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:26.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以就算我也能幫上不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:28.94,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,弗沙裡亞人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:30.86,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是魔法王國的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:38.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜小姐是隸屬于弗沙裡亞魔法王國的正規軍「彩虹之心」大魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:38.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(480,326)}Rainbow Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:38.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(580.915,326)}Arc Wizard
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.89,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,她是天才魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:43.65,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,既然有這麼優秀的人在為什麼由莉佳你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:50.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為 娜娜小姐為了我失去了魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:57.92,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,八個月前 我被真希她們「黑暗彩虹」抓做人質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:57.92,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(383.333,326)}Darkness Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:03.56,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,娜娜小姐為了救我受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:09.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,又為了打倒真希她們解放了自己體內全部的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:16.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這麼做的話就再也沒法使用魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:21.31,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但娜娜小姐為了保護我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.32,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:26.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就繼承了那個人的使命？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:31.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是的 這衣服和手杖原本都是娜娜小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:35.94,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我必須要替娜娜小姐履行她的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.67,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事了 讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見 櫻庭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.39,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:10:00.33,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到會在這里見到弗沙裡亞的古代語術式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:05.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見孝太郎 究竟是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:17.98,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:23.57,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,感覺能明白早苗為什麼會一直這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:33.66,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳  你真的是魔法少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:36.91,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.80,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我周圍有各種各樣的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:40.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:44.96,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但我一直認為只有由莉佳是個普通的女孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:48.33,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,和我一樣是個普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:52.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,和班上傢伙一起犯傻一起吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:57.43,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼都會和你一起平凡的過完這三年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:10:59.62,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,有點自說自話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:04.81,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我一定是希望你只是個普通的同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:10.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,只是有些奇怪興趣的普通同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.06,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥不適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.04,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.00,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:45.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.87,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 一直都沒相信？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:56.30,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這半年的Cosplayer生活也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:11:59.73,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:05.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:09.14,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,孝太郎 你在哪 為什麼一聲不響就走開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.35,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好 控制成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,只是一部分也有相當大的魔力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:24.55,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這樣里見孝太郎就沒法使用那強力離譜的魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.01,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,絕對要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:29.21,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.71,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,把這個房間還給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.32,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,想在這裡打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:38.15,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.64,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.79,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你也是 真希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:50.48,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Mind Flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:55.92,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,吃我這招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.79,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Quick Cast•Force Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.13,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,還行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.89,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Sonic Impact•Modifier•Touch Trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Quick•Double Cast•Acceleration
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.24,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Tiny Memory Flash•Modifier•Touch Trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:15.60,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,請小心點 只要被擦到 就會被奪走幾秒的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.38,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:23.70,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Control Plant•Modifier•Extend Length Four Times!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.00,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.39,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就是現在 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.37,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.81,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,結果還是要用上這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:40.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:41.53,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,吃驚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.60,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這可是你的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:48.67,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真希控制了106號房的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:49.75,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.26,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.91,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,化作一縷幽魂回到故鄉之地去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:59.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Lightenin Lance•Modifier•Change Element Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:01.90,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,And•High Concentration!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:03.79,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.94,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,接招吧 里見孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:13.19,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Quick Cast•Anti Magic Shield•Modifier•Maximize!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:27.14,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,竟然還活著麼 這樣才對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.15,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.27,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:36.03,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就此別過 永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:42.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,虹野由莉佳 還有里見孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,卡瑪拉 可瑪拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.67,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,在呵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:48.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,靈子力防護罩 集中展開于前方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.65,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,頂回去呵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.07,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,一起上 兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:56.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,呵——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.48,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,奇莉華 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.52,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你們 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.77,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我在真希的結界裡開了一個小洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.46,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧 真希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.19,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,一群不知所謂的人來多少又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:24.10,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,防下剛才的攻擊就以為能贏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:28.58,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,同意 戰鬥裡不攻擊可沒法贏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:34.23,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,青騎士 高收束雷射艦炮射擊 殲滅我眼前的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,如您所願 My Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:41.01,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Quick Cast•Force Shield•Modifier Maximize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:46.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,殿下 這有些過…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:49.66,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,折辱吾騎士之罪 就該以萬死謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:57.35,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就是用盡那個房間的魔力 也才堪堪能防禦住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.28,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,扛住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.94,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不過 也就此結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:09.31,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,青騎士 用主炮攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.12,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.35,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,孝太郎是必須與我一同締造舞臺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:17.67,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我要與之一起生氣 一起歡笑 還要一起締造舞臺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.83,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是竟然有人讓孝太郎受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:22.51,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,決不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:25.73,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就算這樣 難道您想連可樂娜莊也毀掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.99,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,吶 我問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:30.65,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.51,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是真希醬幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:35.46,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:55.43,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這都是群什麼人啊 除了里見孝太郎以外還有如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.66,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,還要打嗎 這次可決不會留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.54,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我們不會怎樣的 投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:10.34,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,至今以來一直都麻煩你了 暮光之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:10.34,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(433.333,326)\fs18}Twilight Wing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:15.46,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifice•Twilight Wing•Precast Spell•Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真希呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.32,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,被她逃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.64,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,大家還好嗎 沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.44,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,又在Cosplay了嗎 由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:40.95,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不是說了在家附近別穿那身打扮晃悠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,要穿社團活動的時候穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.89,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,露絲 我們什麼時候回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:50.56,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不知道啊 感覺好像到剛才為止還在學校上課的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.61,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,感覺跳了一段時間呵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:56.08,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪呵 不可思議呵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.68,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不可能會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.76,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼我家屋頂壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:03.20,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,誰幹的 絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.64,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:18.14,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 彩虹由莉佳身邊有這麼多協助者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:22.81,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,當然最需警戒的還是里見孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 迷上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.76,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,別開這種可怕的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:30.78,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何 也解析出了一部分那個房間的術式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:32.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,還得到了敵人的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.10,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,在我們無法出動的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:37.33,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真希你已經做到最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:43.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但還是用暮光之翼換了他們的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:43.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(290.286,326)\fs18}Twilight Wing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:46.22,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,得重新製作新的法杖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:50.34,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,還有繼續在不引起對方懷疑的情況下的情報收集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.68,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就靠你咯 真希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.11,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見孝太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:04.29,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,只有你一定要我親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.41,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.98,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是海膽啦 海膽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:15.90,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.66,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,別笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.63,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我偏笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見你也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:25.26,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 阿孝也真是幼稚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.46,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:28.81,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是還好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:32.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,櫻庭學姐也把里見約出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.77,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,也感覺兩個人的距離拉近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.38,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,由莉佳 最近怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:48.05,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,感覺都沒什麼精神 還時不時的歎氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:53.62,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,其實還以為某些人終於能理解的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:57.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來卻變成錯覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 那還真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:07.10,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見 假設我想讓你相信我是魔法少女的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.99,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.24,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:14.39,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我想什麼都不需要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:21.13,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,最近感覺無所謂你到底是魔法少女還是Cosplayer了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.50,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,無所謂是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:26.10,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,都那說了那麼多次要你相信我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.36,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我信啊 正是因為相信你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:35.18,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你曾經為了保護櫻庭學姐弄得遍體鱗傷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:39.02,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不記得到底是什麼時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:41.52,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,但是自從看到那次之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:45.28,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就感覺無所謂你到底是不是魔法少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:50.25,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,無論你是什麼身份但都是樂於助人的好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.78,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,沒多少會為別人而犧牲自己的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:57.37,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,無關是魔法少女還是Cosplayer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:01.97,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以你說你是魔法少女的話就那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.86,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,因為你能做到符合魔法少女身份的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.28,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,里見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:16.87,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 所以我才會憧憬櫻庭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.74,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,即使無法成為像娜娜一般的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:22.98,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,也要成為像櫻庭學姐的魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:28.86,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,不過你這冒失的傢伙能使魔法的話還挺讓人擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.67,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以還是希望你只是個Cosplayer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:39.26,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,向陽處和彩虹才適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.79,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,真是過分呢 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:54.57,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,所以由莉佳 以後我要把你當成什麼人才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:58.76,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,我是虹野由莉佳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:03.65,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,是一個寄住在你家的同班女生
Comment: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:06.60,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:36.43,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,喂 阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:37.98,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,來玩集換式卡牌遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:39.94,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼 松平大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:41.42,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,就是用這個來對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:45.51,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你看 這是新發售的甲蟲王者…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:48.59,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,你還真是不吸取教訓啊 阿賢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.82,roku_Default,,0,0,0,,
